{
  "info": {
    "name": "Bolamu — Tests E2E",
    "_postman_id": "bolamu-e2e-2026",
    "description": "Collection de tests automatiques des flows Bolamu (inscription patient, connexion, inscription médecin, admin).\n\nPRÉREQUIS :\n1. Sélectionner un environnement Postman contenant au minimum la variable `base_url` (sinon les variables de collection sont utilisées par défaut).\n2. Pour les requêtes d'upload (form-data, champ `file`), attacher manuellement un fichier `test-document.jpg` dans l'onglet Body → form-data (Postman n'autorise pas l'attache automatique d'un fichier).\n3. Les variables `patient_password` et `admin_password` doivent être renseignées manuellement : le mot de passe patient est reçu par SMS après l'inscription, et le mot de passe admin est connu de l'administrateur.\n\nNOTE : l'inscription d'un numéro déjà existant renvoie un statut 409. Changez les numéros (`patient_phone`, `doctor_phone`) pour rejouer les flows d'inscription.\n\nVARIABLES auto-remplies par les tests :\n- upload_token (test 1)\n- file_id (test 2)\n- file_id_diploma (test 6)\n- file_id_ordre (test 7)\n- patient_token (test 3)\n- admin_token (test 9)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://api.bolamu.co/api/v1" },
    { "key": "patient_phone", "value": "+242062325478" },
    { "key": "patient_password", "value": "" },
    { "key": "doctor_phone", "value": "+242060000123" },
    { "key": "admin_phone", "value": "+242060000099" },
    { "key": "admin_password", "value": "" },
    { "key": "upload_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "file_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "file_id_diploma", "value": "" },
    { "key": "file_id_ordre", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patient_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "admin_token", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "FLOW 1 — Inscription Patient",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. POST /upload/token (patient)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('upload_token présent', function () { pm.expect(json.upload_token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty; });",
                  "if (json.upload_token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('upload_token', json.upload_token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('upload_token', json.upload_token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{patient_phone}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/upload/token", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["upload", "token"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. POST /upload/secure (carte identité)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('file_id présent', function () { pm.expect(json.file_id).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty; });",
                  "if (json.file_id) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('file_id', json.file_id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('file_id', json.file_id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{upload_token}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Attacher test-document.jpg manuellement" }
              ]
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/upload/secure", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["upload", "secure"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. POST /auth/register/patient",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 ou 201', function () { pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]); });",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('success true', function () { pm.expect(json.success).to.eql(true); });",
                  "pm.test('token présent', function () { pm.expect(json.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty; });",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('patient_token', json.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('patient_token', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{patient_phone}}\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Test\",\n  \"last_name\": \"Bolamu\",\n  \"gender\": \"M\",\n  \"age\": 30,\n  \"city\": \"Brazzaville\",\n  \"documents_file_ids\": { \"id_card\": \"{{file_id}}\" },\n  \"cgu_accepted\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register/patient", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "register", "patient"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
